<div class="wrapper case-study fieldone">

  <section class="case-header">
    <div class="case-header-container container">
      <p class="case-header-client-name">Field One</p>
      <p class="case-header-tagline">More than just looking better.<br>Let&rsquo;s make it work better.</p>
      <p class="case-header-type">Asset management application</p>
    </div>
  </section><!-- END case-header -->

  <section class="case-exec-summary">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="case-exec-summary-text" data-sr="enter left, move 100px">We made FieldOne&rsquo;s asset management web app easy to use and easy on the eyes.</p>
    </div>
  </section><!-- END case-exec-summary -->

  <section class="case-breakdown">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="col one-third" data-sr="enter top, move 50px">
        <p class="case-breakdown-heading">Challenge</p>
        <p class="case-breakdown-summary">Make it easy to use.</p>
        <p class="case-breakdown-detail">FieldOne&rsquo;s asset management product needed a UX overhaul, including a easier interface with an updated design.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="col one-third" data-sr="wait .25s, enter top, move 50px">
        <p class="case-breakdown-heading">Solution</p>
        <p class="case-breakdown-summary">Revamp the UX.</p>
        <p class="case-breakdown-detail">The Brave team designed and built the design/user interface for Field One&rsquo;s core product, including a number of demonstrable improvements for the end user.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="col one-third" data-sr="wait .5s, enter top, move 50px">
        <p class="case-breakdown-heading">Scope</p>

        <ul class="case-breakdown-scope-list">
          <li>Information Architecture</li>
          <li>Interface Design</li>
          <li>Front End Development</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section><!-- END case-breakdown -->

  <section class="case-block not-padded fo-bg-white">
    <div class="inner-block half float-right" data-sr="enter right, move 150px">
      <img class="case-block-image" src="images/fieldone/work-order.svg">
    </div>

    <div class="inner-block half absolute-left vertical-center left-padded">
      <p class="case-block-text-heading short-length">Tracking that makes sense and saves time.</p>
      <p class="case-block-text-subtext short-length">The core users of the product, dispatchers, wanted a product that would make it easier to view and interact with data on the screen. And that&rsquo;s exactly what we delivered.</p>
    </div>
  </section><!-- END case-block -->

  <section class="case-block fo-bg-light-blue">
    <div class="container">
      <img class="case-block-image" src="images/fieldone/devices.svg">
    </div>
  </section><!-- END case-block -->

  <section class="case-block fo-bg-white">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="inner-block two-third" data-sr="enter left, move 100px">
        <img class="case-block-image" src="images/fieldone/houses.svg">
      </div>

      <div class="inner-block one-third absolute-right vertical-center">
        <p class="case-block-text-heading short-length">Coordination from factory to awarehouse</p>
        <p class="case-block-text-subtext short-length">Simplified view that shows high-level availability of assets and resources.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section><!-- END case-block -->

  <section class="case-block fo-bg-dark-blue">
    <div class="container">
      <img class="case-block-image text-below" src="images/fieldone/scheduler-detail.svg">
      <p class="case-block-text-heading medium-length align-center" data-sr>Right place, right time</p>
      <p class="case-block-text-subtext medium-length align-center" data-sr>Created &ldquo;scheduler assistant&rdquo; functionality that relies on natural language (since users prefer not to be addressed like robots) and lets a dispatcher set recurring appointments.</p>
    </div>
  </section><!-- END case-block -->

  <section class="case-block fo-bg-off-white">
    <div class="container">
      <img class="case-block-image text-below" src="images/fieldone/scheduler.svg">
      <p class="case-block-text-heading medium-length align-center" data-sr>Finding what matters most</p>
      <p class="case-block-text-subtext medium-length align-center" data-sr>Improved hierarchy of information that allows dispatchers to quickly identify and prioritize requests, tasks, and resources.</p>
    </div>
  </section><!-- END case-block -->

  <section class="case-block fo-bg-white">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="inner-block two-third" data-sr="enter left, move 100px">
        <img class="case-block-image" src="images/fieldone/boxes.svg">
      </div>

      <div class="inner-block one-third absolute-right vertical-center">
        <p class="case-block-text-heading short-length">Functions that make sense</p>
        <p class="case-block-text-subtext short-length">Reconfigured the core controls into simpler groupings, pairing similar functions to reduce the number of options/decision points for the user (*fewer options leads to improved efficiency).</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section><!-- END case-block -->

  <section class="case-block fo-bg-dark-blue">
    <div class="container">
      <img class="case-block-text-quote-icon" src="images/fieldone/quote.svg" data-sr="enter top, move 75px">
      <p class="case-block-text-quote align-center">&ldquo;Brave helped us turn our application from dated and clunky to modern and easy. Our customers love the changes, and so do we.&rdquo;</p>
      <p class="case-block-text-citation align-center">Daniel Gittler, <em>FieldOne&rsquo;s Director of Enterprise Services</em></p>
    </div>
  </section><!-- END case-block -->

